data.description: Welcome to 27483 Moonstone Place in Moreno Valley, a beautiful gated community of Hyde Park. Upon entering the family room adjoins the spacious kitchen and dining area. The kitchen offers; stainless steel appliances, abundant of white cabinetry and granite countertops with a large sit-down center island. Roomy downstairs den/office is currently being used for a weight lifting room. The upper level includes; four bedrooms, two bathrooms and a generous size laundry room. The lovely master bedroom has a sizable walk-in closet, enclosed bathroom with quartz countertops, white cabinetry, double sinks, and a relaxing soaking tub with a separate shower. Additional features includes; open floor plan, natural bright lighting, new carpet, recessed lighting, owned solar panels and an attached two car garage. Community amenities; gated entry, Pool and spa, barbecue grills, guest parking, and lush landscaping. It's in a prime location with nearby shopping, entertainment, parks, and easy access to walking/running/hiking trails. Come tour this magnificent home!
